I"<p>The Shopping List Card allows you to add, edit, check-off, and clear items from your shopping list.</p>
<p>Setup of the <a href="/integrations/shopping_list/">Shopping List Intent</a> is required</p>
<p class='img'>
<img src='/images/lovelace/lovelace_shopping_list_card.gif' alt='Screenshot of the shopping list card'>
Screenshot of the Shopping List card.
</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">type: shopping-list
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
