</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='title' href='#title'></a> title</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Title of Shopping List</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='theme' href='#theme'></a> theme</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Set to any theme within <code>themes.yaml</code></p>
</span></p></dd></dl>
</div>
